Imports

{% raw %} 
from fastai.vision.all import *
from transcv.visrectrans import VisRecTrans
{% endraw %}

Datasets & Dataloaders

{% raw %} 
path = untar_data(URLs.PETS)
fnames = get_image_files(path/'images')
pat = r'(.+)_\d+.jpg$'
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
item_tfms = RandomResizedCrop(460, min_scale = 0.75, ratio = (1.,1.))
batch_tfms = [*aug_transforms(size = 224, max_warp = 0), Normalize.from_stats(*imagenet_stats)]
bs = 8
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
dls = ImageDataLoaders.from_name_re(path, fnames, pat, batch_tfms = batch_tfms, 
                                   item_tfms = item_tfms, bs = bs)
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
dls.show_batch(max_n=9, figsize=(6,7))
{% endraw %}

ViT model

We create a ViT-Large model using the VisRecTrans class.

{% raw %} 
vis_rec_ob = VisRecTrans('vit_large_patch16_224', dls.c, True)
model = vis_rec_ob.create_model()
vis_rec_ob.initialize(model)
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
learn = Learner(dls, model, loss_func = CrossEntropyLossFlat(), metrics = accuracy).to_fp16()
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
learn.summary()
